name: Gone Stray (Cat Game)
description:
You are a Cat inside a house, your only goal is the "Escape" your owner. In Each Level there is an  open window that can be used to escape the house. Navigate your way through the levels to the open window. There are only three levels Sadly. 

Use WASD to Move and press Esc to Change the Volume of different things.

SUBCRIBE TO ME ON YOUTUBE!

Coding Ryan
